{"tid":1504143,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"快D攪機場集會，等狗鐵停機場快線","createTime":"2019-08-25T08:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T08:51:49.000Z","uid":52265,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f9b89895f3e0a6c220930a6977a851a2c1760d","tid":1504143,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c766e3d2a944059603383646de947ca27c6ccf","tid":1504143,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ab58ae2066b06defb3a03341d55f073cd50aa7","tid":1504143,"uid":216405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24b504e3174c9b14bd215090595a44b63e514820","tid":1504143,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5e45de05575d6b93a18df3838063333dae259b","tid":1504143,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8650f9d4765cebfddd5daaddb09566fa3c730a8a","tid":1504143,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337133921ae9275cc820f6662522ca13f174d682","tid":1504143,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49eb5284a23df63c9f83d50fe50a5f6f8fd5ff8","tid":1504143,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:51:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>逢星期六日 1pm<br />\n你地千其唔好一齊準時入機場呀</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港身為一個國際都會，<br />\n機場就好似香港嘅心臟一樣咁重要。<br />\n每個星期都重擊心臟，<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港仲有命嘅？</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警告你地班人<br />\n千其唔好逢星期六日咁準時1點一齊入機場，<br />\n大嶼山交通會負荷唔到㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時塞住曬成條入機場嘅路，<br />\n搞到遊客同d crew入唔到機場，咁就慘了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇怕又要cancel好多班機⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞完星期六日，<br />\n兩日內cancel同delay左咁多班機，<br />\n又要幾日先回復到正常，<br />\n但係話咁快又到星期六日！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班仆街又出黎塞！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地知唔知機場好慘㗎？？？？？？？<br />\n未回到氣又比人再塞過！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點知你地班人咁有毅力！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道左機場係春袋，<br />\n約好個個星期都準時1pm塞機場，<br />\n痴撚線！！<br />\n長遠黎講對香港經濟一定有好大影響⋯⋯</span></strong><br />\n知唔知機場每秒幾多錢上落！！！<br />\n你地班廢青have no stake in the society㗎，<br />\n做一世都賺唔到咁多錢呀！<br />\n你地短短地搞兩三個星期，<br />\n到時外國政府都一定會忍唔住出聲，<br />\n令到香港政府同商家佬都好頭痕！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我依家強烈譴責你地班暴徒阻住香港經濟發展呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">好人一生平安，<br />\n認同請分享！<br />\n推比全世界知！<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a28f647ebac294c8b660505cc21770f86c9e76","tid":1504143,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T08:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}